history.content:
Hi All,

We are looking to fill an open GSI position for EE126: Probability and Random Processes this term.  The position involves face-to-face time with students in the form of homework parties and office hours and the development of new modules to be used as labs.  

Necessary skills: Probability at the level of EE126 (or equivalent), ability to implement theoretical ideas in code

If interested, please send an email to kabirc@berkeley.edu

Thanks!
